structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
GENERAL PROVISIONS APPLICABLE TO COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS

law.text: Any emergency services board established pursuant to KRS 65.660 to 65.679 shall comply with the provisions of KRS 65A.010 to 65A.090.
law.history: Created 2013 Ky. Acts ch. 40, sec. 23, effective March 21, 2013.
